      "description": "Join 25 million creators making stop motion animation with ease.\nStop Motion Studio is the Apple-featured app for creating stunning stop motion films.\nEnjoy powerful creative tools with no ads, no tracking, and no subscriptions.\n\nStop Motion Studio is the easiest and most powerful stop motion animation maker for iPhone and iPad. Create beautiful animated films with LEGO, clay, drawings, or everyday objects — no experience required.\n\nWhether you’re a beginner or a seasoned animator, Stop Motion Studio gives you everything you need to turn your ideas into motion.\n\nLoved by Millions Worldwide\n\n* Over 25 million creators and counting\n* Rated 4.7 stars with more than 65,000 reviews\n* Featured in Apple’s “Life on iPad” TV commercial\n\n“Stop Motion Studio makes it easy to create your own stop-motion movies.” – The Washington Post\n“Brings out the LEGO moviemaking geek in all of us.” – TechNewsWorld\n\nCreate and Edit with Precision\n\n* Onion skinning and animation guides for perfect alignment\n* Interactive timeline and frame-by-frame editing\n* Copy, paste, cut, and insert frames with ease\n* Rotoscoping: draw over videos for unique effects\n* Built-in drawing tools, text cards, and speech bubbles\n* Erase unwanted objects and add facial expressions or layers\n* Merge frames to simulate motion blur or speed effects\n\nCapture Every Frame\n\n* Full manual camera controls: focus, exposure, ISO, and white balance\n* Timelapse capture mode for automatic shooting\n* Use your Apple Watch or another device as a remote camera\n\nAdd Sound and Style\n\n* Record voiceovers and narration directly in the app\n* Add sound effects, background music, or import from your library\n* Use filters, fades, and transitions for cinematic results\n* Green screen effects let you place characters anywhere\n\nShare Your Masterpiece\n\n* Export your films in 4K or 1080p HD\n* Share directly to YouTube, TikTok, or save as a GIF or iMessage sticker\n* Transfer projects via AirDrop, iCloud, or Dropbox\n* Start on iPhone and finish on Mac — your work stays in sync\n\nLearn and Improve\n\n* Step-by-step tutorials and creative tips included\n* Built-in manual for quick guidance and inspiration\n\nYours to Create\nNo ads. No tracking. No subscriptions.\nYour data stays private and your creativity stays yours.\n\nDownload Stop Motion Studio today.\nJoin millions of creators and bring your imagination to life — one frame at a time.",
